{"tid":1699202,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"罷工 其實起身拎袋走人 就得","createTime":"2019-11-08T03:15:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-08T15:09:45.000Z","uid":181640,"like":689,"dislike":41,"uniUserReply":105,"replies":[{"pid":"ea919e101434cf87d0c26175713e003ba181a68e","tid":1699202,"uid":181640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T03:15:10.000Z","msg":"我知實畀人屌冇計劃 但香港就係因為大家太有顧慮而就玩完<br />\n睇完周同學消息 擺低電話 繼續扮工<br />\n然後話1111見？<br />\n<br />\n只要大家哩一刻 起身 拎袋 走人 就開始左我哋香港嘅罷工<br />\n唔需要啲咩標記 準備<br />\n請假並唔叫罷工<br />\n<br />\n罷一日 兩日 有咩用<br />\n依家哩一刻 一定要開始罷工罷課罷市<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔好再等啦香港人</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9aa34bd3e24f42da61177c8c9a893f4b8a2510b3","tid":1699202,"uid":181640,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T03:15:47.000Z","msg":"自推十連"},{"pid":"ed8ffe3a1f583021710badd7a59921e56c903de3","tid":1699202,"uid":181640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T03:16:00.000Z","msg":"10/10"},{"pid":"dc6cb75021836e0c6b0e6cb4b99e27bcc0ba0748","tid":1699202,"uid":181640,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T03:16:13.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"0db98dda7e4cbb94241dcd163db46f1272faccec","tid":1699202,"uid":113525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T03:16:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cd3294ffea8239168f8fe2312888d4b78d8c75fa","tid":1699202,"uid":181640,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T03:16:23.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"920c3c6efa56b814d761738b474e56182563bd3d","tid":1699202,"uid":124859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T03:16:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d280ee028dcce289ad645977